question: Within a radius of 70 kilometers, where can I find  a restaurant along the way to Memory Garden, Baltimore, MD from Cal, Sr.'s Yard, Aberdeen, MD?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-76.186327 39.533089)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-76.638575 39.300016)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-76.186327 39.533089)',4326)::geography, 70000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-76.186327 39.533089)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
